data.description: This very nice home is 20 minutes from uptown Charlotte and 5 minutes from quaint uptown Mount Holly. This nice 3 year old 2 story home is like new and has been well cared for since its construction with a low maintenance vinyl exterior. The main level features an open floor plan with a drop zone as you enter from the 2 car garage. The kitchen features an abundance of cabinet space, large island and granite countertops. The main level flex room can be used as an office, workout area or anything your imagination desires. The upper level features a loft, the Master, and 2 secondary bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and walk-in closet. The home is built on a deep cleared lot that backs to a wooded area which enhances privacy. Please call for an appointment.
